How to run

- Ensure Python 3.9+ is installed.
- Install Flask: pip install flask
- Save files respecting the shown directory structure:
  - app.py
  - sudoku.py
  - templates/index.html
  - static/js/main.js
  - static/css/styles.css
- Run: python app.py
- Open browser at http://127.0.0.1:5000

Features implemented

- 9x9 Sudoku board with given cells and editable cells.
- Client-side rule checking to highlight row/column/box conflicts.
- Server-side mistake checking against the canonical solution.
- Completion verification confirming when the puzzle is solved.
- New puzzle generation with difficulty-aware removals and uniqueness checking, plus a reliable fallback puzzle.

